/*
Call this script from a workflow transition post-function.
It will increment the value of a numerical custom field.

The user is expected to modify the following fields to match their Jira
instance:
* "2.5" (whatever decimal value you'd like to add to a numeric field)
* customfield_10000 (customField)
*/

number increment = 2.5;
customfield_10000 += increment;
